{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/book/2020/06/07/在WSL2安装Keras及其依赖.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"12478abe-3497-561c-a12c-9860687aa71c","excerpt":"在 WSL2 安装 Keras 及其依赖 安装 python 首先安装 python3 和 pip3，并且使用 USTC 源。 安装 python 科学套件 安装 BLAS 库（OpenBLAS），确保可以在 CPU 上面做张量运算。 安装 Python 科学套件：Numpy、SciPy 和 Matplotlib…","html":"<h1>在 WSL2 安装 Keras 及其依赖</h1>\n<h2>安装 python</h2>\n<p>首先安装 python3 和 pip3，并且使用 USTC 源。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> python3 python3-pip python3-dev\npip3 <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -i https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/pypi/web/simple pip -U\npip3 config <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">set</span> global.index-url https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/pypi/web/simple</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2>安装 python 科学套件</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>安装 BLAS 库（OpenBLAS），确保可以在 CPU 上面做张量运算。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> build-essential cmake <span class=\"token function\">git</span> <span class=\"token function\">unzip</span> pkg-config libopenblas-dev liblapack-dev</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装 Python 科学套件：Numpy、SciPy 和 Matplotlib。这是做科学计算必须的。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> python3-numpy python3-scipy python3-matplotlib python3-yaml</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装 HDF5，最初由 NASA 开发，用于保存数值数据的大文件。它可以帮助 Keras 模型快速高效保存到磁盘。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> libhdf5-serial-dev python3-h5py</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装 Graphviz 和 pydot-ng，这两个包用于可视化 Keras 模型。并不是必须的。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> graphviz\npip3 <span class=\"token function\">install</span> pydot-ng</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装 tensorflow</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">pip3 <span class=\"token function\">install</span> tensorflow\npip3 <span class=\"token function\">install</span> tensorflow-gpu</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>安装 Keras</h2>\n<p>使用 pip3 安装 Keras。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">pip3 <span class=\"token function\">install</span> keras</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>可以从 GitHub 中下载 Keras 的例子</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone https://github.com/keras-team/keras.git</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>测试一个例子</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">python3 mnist_cnn.py</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>执行成功后会在<code class=\"language-text\">~/.keras/keras.json</code>生成配置文件。</p>","frontmatter":{"category":"book"},"fields":{"slug":"/book/2020/06/07/在WSL2安装Keras及其依赖.html","date":"June 07, 2020","title":"在WSL2安装Keras及其依赖"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/book/2020/06/07/在WSL2安装Keras及其依赖.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/book/2020/06/06/读「Python深度学习」数学基础.html","title":"读「Python深度学习」数学基础"},"frontmatter":{"category":"book"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/book/2020/06/08/Keras分类问题-电影评论分类.html","title":"Keras分类问题-电影评论分类"},"frontmatter":{"category":"book"}}}}}